<item>
            <title>[LU-5488] lustre test should not assume path to binaries consistent across cluster</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5488</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In some cases, ie el7 vs el6, the path to commands (lctl, lfs...) are different. In particular starting el7 /sbin is symlinked to /usr/sbin so the path could be /sbin not /usr/sbin. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
